to him the<BR>
complexities of the task he was asking of us.<BR>
I contacted my affiliate in Amsterdam and had the funds available.<BR>
I undertook all the processes and made sure I followed his precise =
instructions to<BR>
the letter and had the funds deposited at a Amsterdam based security and =
consultancy firm.<BR>
This Asset Management firm is a specialised private firm that accepts =
deposits from high<BR>
net worth individuals and blue chip corporations that handle valuable =
products or<BR>
undertake transactions that need immediate access to cash. This small =
and highly private<BR>
organization is familiar especially to the highly placed and =
well-connected organizations.<BR>
In line with his instructions, the money was deposited with an Asset =
Management firm.<BR>
Mr. RALPH BRINK told me he wanted the money there in anticipation of his =
arrival from<BR>
England later that week. This was the last communication we had, this =
transpired around<BR>
25th February 2004.<BR>
<BR>
