alone have the<BR>
deposit details and they will release the deposit to no one unless I =
instruct them to do so.<BR>
I alone know of the existence of this deposit for as far as ABN/AMRO is =
concerned,<BR>
the transaction with Mr. RALPH BRINK concluded when I deposited the =
